  "detailed_description": "Esports History is an RPG sim where you start as a regular guy, and work your way up to the very top of esports. Defeat bosses in tournaments, make a name for yourself within the esports community, and become a real pro!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IN-DEPTH MINI-GAMES</h2>Choose between strategies and shooters. Play engrossing mini-games inspired by iconic hits. You can choose between manual or automatic mode.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/933ae2df331a9d7a47ea41c96feb375d.poster.avif?t=1727960449\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/933ae2df331a9d7a47ea41c96feb375d.webm?t=1727960449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE YOUR RESOURCES WISELY</h2>Manage your time, earn money, and practice at PC clubs. But don't forget to rest and monitor your stress level to make sure you don't fall behind in the race to be the best.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/4ee465a69f3adebb67d985d879c77cc9.poster.avif?t=1727960449\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/4ee465a69f3adebb67d985d879c77cc9.webm?t=1727960449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PUT TOGETHER A UNIQUE BUILD</h2>Use a flexible talent system and choose which stats to upgrade through practice to become an unbeatable player.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/ab335d7a1fad9e930a7bc6f0115e6968.poster.avif?t=1727960449\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/ab335d7a1fad9e930a7bc6f0115e6968.webm?t=1727960449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JOIN A COMMUNITY OF GAMERS</h2>Dive into gaming hangouts, where rivalries abound and friendships can be found in unexpected places.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/94ce7e7ae8733e1e9643908b50839735.poster.avif?t=1727960449\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/94ce7e7ae8733e1e9643908b50839735.webm?t=1727960449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ESPORTS ADVENTURE</h2>Pave your way to glory! Complete quests, face the odds, and challenge the most skillful players on the way to your dream.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/c439058004a1363c655189bc8681c8c9.poster.avif?t=1727960449\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/c439058004a1363c655189bc8681c8c9.webm?t=1727960449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Esports History is an RPG sim where you start as a regular guy, and work your way up to the very top of esports. Defeat bosses in tournaments, make a name for yourself within the esports community, and become a real pro!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IN-DEPTH MINI-GAMES</h2>Choose between strategies and shooters. Play engrossing mini-games inspired by iconic hits. You can choose between manual or automatic mode.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/933ae2df331a9d7a47ea41c96feb375d.poster.avif?t=1727960449\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/933ae2df331a9d7a47ea41c96feb375d.webm?t=1727960449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE YOUR RESOURCES WISELY</h2>Manage your time, earn money, and practice at PC clubs. But don't forget to rest and monitor your stress level to make sure you don't fall behind in the race to be the best.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/4ee465a69f3adebb67d985d879c77cc9.poster.avif?t=1727960449\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/4ee465a69f3adebb67d985d879c77cc9.webm?t=1727960449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PUT TOGETHER A UNIQUE BUILD</h2>Use a flexible talent system and choose which stats to upgrade through practice to become an unbeatable player.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742360/extras/ab335d7a1fad9e9